# === SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH (2026-02-25) ===
# Policy: One .md per folder, under 250KB, for human readability.
# CLAUDE.md is the sole root exception.
# All evidence is JSON-first in apps/mcp-server/data/evidence/.
# Allowed .md files:
#   CLAUDE.md (root), README.md (root), .claude/PRINCIPLES.md,
#   docs/AGENT_GUIDE.md, apps/mcp-server/DATABASE_MIGRATION_NOTES.md,
#   .github/actions/setup-terraform-vars/README.md
*.md
!CLAUDE.md
!README.md
!.claude/PRINCIPLES.md
!docs/AGENT_GUIDE.md
!apps/mcp-server/DATABASE_MIGRATION_NOTES.md
!.github/actions/setup-terraform-vars/README.md
!apps/mcp-server/data/evidence/2026-02/PRODUCTION_READINESS_ROADMAP_2026-02-13.md
!apps/mcp-server/data/evidence/milestone-2026-01-29/SESSION_SUMMARY_2026-01-29.md
!docs/architecture/ECTROPY-ENVIRONMENT-ARCHITECTURE-2026-04-08.md

